These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-1::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  analyst, firefighter, nurse, pilot, security-guard, social-worker
City: marseilles, paris, nizza, san-francisco, london, new-york
1. the pilot is on the left of the nurse##1
2. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the social-worker##1
3. the analyst is on the left of the firefighter##1
4. the person traveling to london is between the social-worker and the person traveling to marseilles##2
5. the person traveling to san-francisco is between the person traveling to london and the person traveling to paris##2
6. the person traveling to marseilles is the pilot##1
7. the security-guard is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
8. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the firefighter##1
9. the security-guard is on the right of the social-worker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |       3       |       4        |    5     |   6    |
| Job           | analyst | firefighter | social-worker | security-guard | pilot    | nurse  |
| City   | new-york | paris   | san-francisco       | london        | marseilles | nizza |

