.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-2::.
There are 6 different nationalities: argentine, dutch, german, italian, thai, turkish
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: comedy, animation, musical, martial-arts, crime, zombie
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
2. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the thai##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is between the italian and the argentine##2
4. the german is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
5. the argentine is on the far right##1
6. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
7. the italian is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
8. the dutch is on the left of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |  3   |    4    |   5    |     6      |
| Nationality   | dutch | turkish | thai | italian | german | argentine  |
| Movie-Genre           | zombie | crime  | comedy | animation    | martial-arts  | musical |

