.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-3::.
6 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, frog, guinea-pig, rabbit, snake
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: november, september, december, july, october, march
1. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person who's birthday is in october##1
3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the owner of the frog is on the far right##1
6. the owner of the rabbit is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the person who's birthday is in november##2
7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left##1
8. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
9. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| Pet         | chinchilla | bird | snake      | rabbit | guinea-pig | frog      |
| Birthday   | september    | march  | november | july   | october       | december |

