.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-4::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, alhambra, chaman, baccarat, montecristo, tiparillo
The people use 6 different means of transport: bike, quad-bike, roller, scooter, taxi, trike
1. the person driving the roller is the baccarat-smoker##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
4. the person driving the scooter is the alhambra-smoker##1
5. the swisher-smoker is the person driving the bike##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person driving the bike and the tiparillo-smoker##2
7. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
8. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |   6    |
| Cigar        | alhambra    | tiparillo | chaman | swisher | montecristo | baccarat   |
| Transport   | scooter | taxi        | quad-bike  | bike     | trike  | roller |

