.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-6::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: green, pink, red, blue, coral, purple
The people have 6 different hobbies: board-games, card-games, dancing, reading, traveling, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person who likes pink##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
5. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
6. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
7. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person who likes purple##1
8. the person who likes red is between the person who likes blue and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
9. the person who likes green is the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5     |      6      |
| Color    | green | purple | coral  | blue      | red | pink  |
| Hobby   | card-games  | dancing    | reading | board-games | traveling | woodworking |

