3. the person who growsdaffodil is between the person who growsazalea and the person who growsbegonia##2
4. the musician is the person who growssunflower##1
5. the mechanic is between the journalist and the social-worker##2
6. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
7. the social-worker is on the right of the teacher##1
8. the social-worker is on the right of the teacher##1
9. the mechanic is on the right of the person who growsrose##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |     5      |    6     |
