.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-9::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: chess, filmmaking, gardening, hiking, singing, sudoku
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: musical, romance, thriller, fantasy, western, horror
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 2. the person watching musical movies is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person watching horror movies##2
 3. the person watching romance movies is on the far left##1
 4. the person watching fantasy movies is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
 6. the person watching fantasy movies is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 7. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 8. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 9. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
10. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |     3      |   4    |   5    |       6       |
| Hobby   | chess   | singing  | filmmaking | hiking | sudoku | gardening     |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | musical | horror    | western | fantasy | thriller |

