.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-13::.
There are 6 different favourite colors: black, blood-red, apricot, pink, yellow, light-blue
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: classical, country, house, r&b, soul, trance
1. the fan of house is on the far left##1
2. the person who likes black is on the right of the fan of trance##1
3. the fan of classical is between the person who likes yellow and the person who likes pink##2
4. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the fan of country##1
5. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the fan of trance##1
6. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of country##1
7. the fan of r&b is the person who likes black##1
8. the person who likes yellow is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |     5     |  6   |
| Color          | apricot | blood-red | black | yellow    | light-blue | pink |
| Music-Genre   | house     | trance | r&b   | country | classical | soul |

