6 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, bluemaster, game, chaman, alhambra, aristoff
 1. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person eating peas##1
 2. the aristoff-smoker is between the alhambra-smoker and the person eating banana##2
 3. the alhambra-smoker is between the person eating zucchini and the bongani-smoker##2
 4. the game-smoker is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
 5. the person eating zucchini is between the game-smoker and the person eating mango##2
 6. the person eating onion is the bluemaster-smoker##1
 7. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person eating banana##1
 8. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
 9. the person eating peas is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
10. the person eating onion is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4     |       5        |      6       |
| Food   | onion     | avocado | peas   | mango     | zucchini       | banana       |
| Cigar    | bluemaster | chaman   | bongani | alhambra | aristoff | game |

