.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-15::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: classical, disco, metal, pop, r&b, trance
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: skateboarding, weightlifting, snowboarding, swimming, handball, skiing
 1. the fan of trance is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the person who's sport is handball and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
 4. the fan of classical is on the far right##1
 5. the fan of r&b is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 6. the fan of metal is the person who's sport is handball##1
 7. the fan of pop is the fan of pop##1
 8. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 9. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
10. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |   5    |     6     |
| Music-Genre   | trance | r&b    | metal     | disco      | pop    | classical |
| Sport   | weightlifting | skateboarding | handball | snowboarding | skiing | swimming  |

