.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-16::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, fanta, juice, sprite, tea
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: november, march, april, december, july, august
1. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
3. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person drinking cola##2
5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left##1
7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
8. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |      3       |   4    |     5      |    6    |
| Beverage   | sprite   | coffee   | fanta        | cola   | tea        | juice   |
| Birthday      | november | july | december | april | august | march |

