 6. the turkish is on the right of the italian##1
 7. the chinese is the person drinking fanta##1
 8. the russian is on the right of the british##1
 9. the dutch is between the person drinking milk and the person drinking cola##2
10. the person drinking iced-tea is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3      |      4      |       5       |    6    |
| Beverage         | hot-chocolate | cola | sprite | milk | iced-tea | fanta |
| Nationality   | british | russian | dutch      | italian     | turkish       | chinese |

 